Mozilla Observatory Addon is dead, Site Security Toolkit is alive
------------------

I have expanded my Firefox addon to allow scanning with a bunch of sites. I also mis-spelled the name on the first submission to [AMO](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/) so the tooklit is alive I guess!

Available at <https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/site-security-tooklit/>


